author: Emer - Kildare
title: Emer - Kildare
text: Great shopping experience. Came across this store on line because I needed a specific bracelet. Bought a few more items. One was out of stock and a very pleasant girl rang me. Account was credited. Goods arrived next day, lovely packaging. Very impressed.
